message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product to you for $12,000. I believe it offers significant value at this price point.
Hello Alice, thank you for the offer. I understand the value of the product, but I am only able to pay up to $10,000 for it. I hope we can come to an agreement.
Hi Bob, I appreciate your offer.  I'm willing to come down a bit, how about $11,000?
Hello Alice, thank you for adjusting your offer. I appreciate it. However, I am still unable to meet you at $11,000. I would like to propose $9,500 for the product.
